{"tid":460140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子致電話機上有炸彈，因航緊急疏散乘客","createTime":"2017-11-06T11:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T23:38:25.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d86b55017bcb1568cca345f1bfd84ec6ef7faef4","tid":460140,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"因航一部CX751客機，原定於下午2時20分由香港出發前往泰國曼谷，據消息稱，起飛前有一名女子致電機管局的熱線報稱CX751機上有炸彈，因航隨即疏散機上所有乘客，以及把行李移離飛機。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，經初步調查，未有在機上發現任何可疑物品或爆炸品。受事件影響，CX751預計於今日傍晚6時再出發前往目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁兒嬉？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁咪可以身在外國日日打長途電話去hotline，聲稱因航有炸彈？"},{"pid":"b13bc6f0b3097713546d7e5aafa142a267b2e2c5","tid":460140,"uid":10975,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"你講野仲撚兒戲啦"},{"pid":"8c4df6f08e8cd85a9499055563e174939d9b9e2c","tid":460140,"uid":6063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"影響航空安全係國際法黎，唔係香港唔代表告唔到你架"},{"pid":"7b8a0eb11a5715138fedb54a27c0a1a3d15ffe1a","tid":460140,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"你可以試下"},{"pid":"4cb0e0cee834a52c889e014fbe8de83d46fb19f1","tid":460140,"uid":55231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"唔撚check就真係兒戲啦"},{"pid":"a8410a0c2b2d13f61e89893e88bba62e1c9e1416","tid":460140,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影響航空安全係國際法黎，唔係香港唔代表告唔到你架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會call國際刑警？"},{"pid":"9358ff1c68526af413c300bc2b1ee35e03575f7c","tid":460140,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:28:47.000Z","msg":"樓主真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239fb01bdba3fb81fb2a93c8f7a5ce21152cec9c","tid":460140,"uid":22553,"like":0